0.0.2
-----
1. Wait for 5 seconds for URL to load. If an invalid server address is entered
   then this will timeout.
2. Auto-detect LMS server.
3. Add button in settings dialog to detect other servers. First one found that
   is not the current server is used.
4. Show server name and address in settings dialog.

